@startuml
title Component Diagram: Edge-to-Cloud Kafka System

package "Edge Application" {
  component "Event Generator" as Gen
  component "Kafka Producer Adapter" as Prod

  Gen --> Prod : create event
}

package "Server Application" {
  component "Kafka Consumer Adapter" as Cons
  component "Data Handler" as Handler
  component "Flask API" as API

  Cons --> Handler : deliver event
  Handler --> API : expose data
}

component "Kafka Broker" as Kafka

Prod --> Kafka : produce(JSON)
Kafka --> Cons : consume(JSON)

note right of Prod
Uses confluent-kafka Producer
end note

note right of Cons
Uses confluent-kafka Consumer
end note

@enduml

